value.0: The Imperial Guard's Armor is light yet heavily padded crimson and black armor that provides protection against physical attacks. Their sophisticated battle helmet, which is lined with advanced sensors, allows them to work in complete darkness, and also contains a comlink scrambler for communication with fellow personnel. A unit commander's helmet is also equipped with a voice activated heads-up display that shows Coruscant Guard positions. Optional tracking beacon software lets a unit commander know the whereabouts of his subordinates at all times.
